+ * @param type - Widget type (e.g., 'm.call').
+ * @param url - Widget URL.
+ * @param waitForIframeLoad - Whether to wait for iframe load signal.
+ * @param data - Widget data.
+ * @param roomId - Room ID.
+ * @returns The IApp widget definition.
